ly, just as a quality assurance team cannot build a high-quality product but can identify flaws, a high-quality HR team cannot directly create a stellar company culture but can highlight when leadership and management are falling short.\",\"type\":\"untitled\"},{\"hierarchy\":[{\"content\":\"**THE EMPLOYEE LIFE CYCLE**\",\"index\":806,\"type\":\"markdown\",\"summarizable\":true},{\"hierarchy\":[{\"hierarchy\":[{\"content\":\"The best way to approach management quality assurance is through the lens of the employee life cycle. From hire to retire, how good is your company? Is your management team world-class in all phases? How do you know?\",\"index\":807,\"type\":\"markdown\",\"summarizable\":true},{\"content\":\"A great HR organization will support, measure, and help improve your management team. Some of the questions they will help you answer:\",\"index\":808,\"type\":\"markdown\",\"summarizable\":true}],\"summary\":\"The most effective way to approach management quality assurance is by examining the employee life cycle, from hire to retire. Is your company excelling in every phase? How can you be certain? A top-tier HR organization will support, measure, and enhance your management team. They help answer crucial questions around performance and improvement, ensuring your management is world-class at every step.\",\"type\":\"untitled\"},{\"hierarchy\":[{\"content\":\"**Recruiting and Hiring**\",\"index\":809,\"type\":\"markdown\",\"summarizable\":true},{\"content\":\"* Do you sharply understand the skills and talents required to succeed in every open position?\\n\\n* Are your interviewers well prepared?\\n\\n* Do your managers and employees do an effective job of selling your company to prospective employees?\\n\\n* Do interviewers arrive on time?\\n\\n* Do managers and recruiters follow up with candidates in a timely fashion?\\n\\n* Do you compete effectively for talent against the best companies?\",\"index\":810,\"type\":\"markdown\",\"summarizable\":true}],\"sum